INSERT INTO "brand_profiles" VALUES('1764354641235-kpbc6myp5','www.apple.com','Apple','Discover the innovative world of Apple','Apple is a technology company that designs and manufactures innovative consumer electronics, software, and services. The brand has built its reputation on creating seamlessly integrated products that combine cutting-edge technology with elegant design.','To create innovative products that enrich people''s lives through technology','Apple positions itself as a premium technology innovator that delivers powerful, beautifully designed products with seamless integration across devices. They emphasize innovation, quality, and the user experience as core differentiators in a competitive market.','["Innovative technology with elegant design","Seamless ecosystem integration across devices","Premium quality and performance","Comprehensive support and services","Trade-in and financing options for accessibility"]','["Innovative","Confident","Minimalist","Premium","Approachable"]','{"formal":65,"playful":25,"premium":85,"technical":60,"energetic":70}','["All out Pro","The thinnest iPhone ever","The world''s best","The ultimate way","supercharged","innovative","powerful","Stream now","Learn more"]','["Cheap","Budget","Basic","Ordinary","Complicated","Excessive marketing jargon"]','Tech-savvy professionals and consumers aged 18-55 who value innovation, design quality, and seamless technology integration. They are willing to invest in premium products and appreciate ecosystem lock-in benefits.','["Powerful, reliable devices for work and personal use","Seamless integration across multiple devices","Premium design and build quality","Comprehensive support and services","Access to exclusive entertainment and services"]','["Device fragmentation and incompatibility","High upfront costs of premium technology","Need for reliable customer support","Desire for latest technology without complete device replacement","Balancing productivity with entertainment needs"]','{"sentenceLength":"short","paragraphStyle":"Apple uses extremely concise copy, often single sentences or short phrases. Product descriptions are punchy and benefit-focused rather than feature-heavy. Paragraphs rarely exceed 2-3 lines.","formatting":"Heavy use of short headlines followed by descriptive subheadings. Call-to-action buttons are prominent (''Learn more'', ''Buy'', ''Stream now''). Product names and key features are bolded or emphasized. Lists are minimal; instead, they use scannable short phrases.","avoid":["Long, complex sentences","Excessive technical jargon without context","Superlatives without substantiation","Cluttered layouts with too much text","Casual or overly playful tone in product descriptions","Generic marketing speak"]}',1764354641,1764354641);
INSERT INTO "brand_profiles" VALUES('1764612908983-fe457pnt6','www.eosfitness.com','E≈çS Fitness','Better Gym. Better Price.','E≈çS Fitness operates High Value. Low Price. (HVLP)¬Æ gyms designed to be accessible to everyone and welcoming to anyone. The brand combines premium fitness amenities with affordable membership options to democratize fitness.','Make premium health and fitness amenities accessible to everyone at an affordable price','E≈çS positions itself as a premium gym experience at an accessible price point, offering serious fitness equipment and amenities without the premium price tag. They compete on value, cleanliness, variety, and community rather than exclusivity.','["Premium amenities at affordable monthly rates starting at $9.99","Extensive equipment variety including free weights, Olympic platforms, cardio, pools, and specialized spaces","Flexible membership tiers (Will Do, Will Crush, Will Power) to match different fitness levels and budgets","200+ gym locations providing accessibility and travel flexibility","Expert personal training and group fitness classes included or available","Unique amenities like MOVE≈çS Cinema, indoor pools, basketball courts, and outdoor gym spaces"]','["Energetic and motivational","Approachable and inclusive","Confident without being pretentious","Playful with wordplay","Action-oriented"]','{"formal":25,"playful":75,"premium":60,"technical":35,"energetic":85}','["Flex your muscles, stretch your wallet","Will Power","Will Crush","Will Do","Fit Fam","Fully Stacked","Get Serious","Ignite your workout","Feelin'' the Love","Unbeatably low","Unstoppable you","Level up","Build yourself up","Awesome workout"]','["Luxury gym","Elite membership","Exclusive access","Premium only","High-end facilities","Corporate jargon","Overly technical fitness terminology"]','Budget-conscious fitness enthusiasts aged 13+ who want serious gym equipment and amenities without premium pricing. Includes casual fitness seekers, travelers, busy profe