INSERT INTO "brand_profiles" VALUES('1764627319118-gikq29zro','www.crunch.com','Crunch Fitness','#NOJUDGMENTS','Crunch Fitness is a global gym chain with a strong presence across multiple countries including the United States, Australia, Canada, Costa Rica, Spain, and Portugal. The brand has established itself as an inclusive fitness community with locations like North Richland Hills, TX that combine state-of-the-art equipment with a welcoming, non-judgmental atmosphere.','Making serious fitness fun and accessible to everyone, regardless of shape, size, age, race, gender, ability, or fitness level, while providing a supportive community and expert coaching to help members achieve their fitness goals.','Crunch positions itself as an inclusive, judgment-free gym that combines affordability with premium amenities and expert coaching. Unlike traditional gyms, Crunch emphasizes fun, community, and flexibility while offering industry-leading equipment and specialized programs like HIITZone.','["Affordable membership starting at $9.99/month with no long-term contracts","Inclusive, non-judgmental community welcoming all fitness levels","Advanced HIIT training through proprietary HIITZone program","Diverse group fitness classes led by energetic instructors","Relax & Recover services including HydroMassage and tanning","Certified personal trainers for one-on-one guidance","Multi-club access options for flexibility and convenience","Member perks including free t-shirt, bring-a-friend privileges, and babysitting"]','["Playful and energetic","Inclusive and welcoming","Motivational and empowering","Fun-loving and approachable","Confident without being pretentious"]','{"formal":25,"playful":85,"premium":60,"technical":35,"energetic":90}','["#NOJUDGMENTS","No Judgments","gym-azing","exer-citing","perspiring to greatness","drop it like it''s hot","high-fives","sweat sesh","get pumped","break a sweat","achieve results","look & feel your best","fitness fun","edge-of-your-seat","can''t-get-enough","work up a sweat","shiny stuff. Heavy stuff. Tons of stuff","ahhh-mazing","gym-improve","Crunch difference"]','["Overly technical fitness jargon without explanation","Formal corporate language","Generic gym terminology without personality","Negative framing or shame-based messaging"]','Fitness-conscious individuals of all levels (beginners to experienced) aged 18-55 who value affordability, flexibility, and a judgment-free environment. Includes busy professionals, parents, and people seeking community-based fitness without long-term commitment.','["Affordable gym membership without long-term contracts","Welcoming, non-judgmental fitness environment","Variety of workout options from cardio to HIIT to group classes","Expert guidance through personal trainers and group instructors","Recovery and wellness amenities","Flexible scheduling that fits their lifestyle","Community and social connection through fitness","Childcare options for parents"]','["Intimidation or judgment at traditional gyms","Long-term contracts and hidden fees","Limited class variety or outdated equipment","Lack of flexibility to pause or cancel membership","Difficulty finding time to work out with family obligations","Uncertainty about commitment before joining","High membership costs relative to perceived value"]','{"sentenceLength":"short to medium","paragraphStyle":"Mix of short punchy sentences for emphasis with medium-length explanatory sentences. Frequent use of sentence fragments for impact. Paragraphs are typically 2-4 sentences, occasionally longer for detailed benefit explanations. Heavy use of bullet points and lists for scanability.","formatting":"Extensive use of bold text for emphasis, ALL CAPS for key phrases, bullet points for feature lists, short headers with descriptive subheaders, emojis avoided but playful punctuation used (exclamation marks, ampersands). Content organized in clear sections with visual hierarchy.","avoid":["Overly long, complex sentences","Passive voice when active is available","Clich√©d fitness language without personality","Shame-based or negative messaging","Emojis or excessive punctuation","Jargon without explanation","Formal corporate tone"]}',1764627319,1764627319);
INSERT INTO "brand_profiles" VALUES('1764669794406-43fvrk2uu','www.amazon.com','Amazon','For Her - Online shopping from a great selection','Amazon is a global e-commerce platform that has expanded to serve diverse customer segments with curated shopping experiences. The ''For Her'' store represents Amazon''s targeted approach to providing personalized shopping destinations for specific audiences.','To be Earth''s most customer-centric company where people can find and discover anything they want to buy online','Amazon positions itself as a comprehensive, convenient online marketplace offering vast selection across categories with fast delivery, competitive pricing, and customer-focused services. The ''For Her'' vertical targets female shoppers with curated gift and lifestyle product selections.','["Vast selection across multiple categories from budget to premium","Fast and free shipping options including next-day delivery","Competitive pricing with frequent deals and Subscribe & Save discounts","Curated collections and gift guides for specific audiences","Customer reviews and ratings to inform purchase decisions","Prime membership benefits and loyalty programs"]','["Practical and helpful","Customer-centric","Efficient and straightforward","Inclusive and accessible","Solution-oriented"]','{"formal":65,"playful":25,"premium":55,"technical":40,"energetic":50}','["Shop all","Get it fast","FREE delivery","Or fastest delivery","Only X left in stock","100+ bought in past month","Limited time deal","Save X% with Subscribe & Save","Delivering to","Top Gifts for Her","Our Top 100+"]','["Flowery marketing language","Excessive exclamation marks","Vague claims without data","Overly casual slang","Emotional manipulation tactics"]','Female shoppers aged 18-65 seeking gifts, personal care products, fashion, home goods, and lifestyle items. Includes both budget-conscious and premium buyers, gift-givers looking for curated recommendations, and Prime members seeking convenience.','["Convenient access to diverse product categories in one place","Curated gift recommendations and inspiration","Fast delivery and flexible shipping options","Competitive pricing and discount opportunities","Trusted product reviews and social proof","Easy navigation and filtering by price, category, and ratings"]','["Decision paralysis from overwhelming product selection","Difficulty finding appropriate gifts for specific recipients","Uncertainty about product quality without reviews","Time constraints for shopping and delivery","Budget limitations requiring price transparency","Need for personalized shopping experiences"]','{"sentenceLength":"short","paragraphStyle":"Minimal paragraph usage; content is primarily organized through navigation menus, category listings, and product cards. Information is presented in scannable, modular chunks rather than flowing prose.","formatting":"Heavy use of hierarchical headings, category navigation, product cards with images and ratings, price displays, delivery information, and action buttons. Bullet-point style filtering options. Minimal body copy.","avoid":["Long narrative descriptions","Flowery adjectives without context","Assumptions about customer preferences","Overly technical product specifications without benefits","Inconsistent pricing presentation","Unclear call-to-action language"]}',1764669794,1764669794);
INSERT INTO "brand_profiles" VALUES('1764690346864-u03zicbt8','www.planetfitness.com','Planet Fitness','Judgement Free Zone‚Ñ¢','Planet Fitness has grown to 2,700+ locations worldwide, establishing itself as an accessible fitness brand that welcomes everyone regardless of fitness level or experience.','To make fitness accessible and welcoming to all by providing affordable memberships, free fitness training, and a non-judgmental environment where members feel comfortable pursuing their health goals.','Planet Fitness positions itself as the affordable, inclusive alternative to premium gyms. They emphasize accessibility through low monthly costs ($15+), no commitment options, and a deliberately welcoming ''Judgement Free Zone'' culture that appeals to first-time gym users and fitness veterans alike.','["Affordable membership starting at $15/month with flexible commitment options","Free fitness training included with membership from certified trainers","Judgement Free Zone‚Ñ¢ - welcoming, non-intimidating environment for all fitness levels","State-of-the-art equipment and amenities including cardio, strength, and functional training","Premium perks for Black Card members including access to 2,700+ worldwide locations, massage chairs, HydroMassage‚Ñ¢, and guest privileges","Convenient digital access through PF mobile app with workout videos and fitness tracking"]','["Welcoming and inclusive","Approachable and friendly","Encouraging without being pushy","Practical and straightforward","Non-judgmental and supportive"]','{"formal":35,"playful":55,"premium":40,"technical":45,"energetic":65}','["Judgement Free Zone‚Ñ¢","We don''t judge","get started","home in our","working out is better with a buddy","make it easy","state-of-the-art","fitness veterans","first-time gym user","step up your workout","get the most out of your workouts","work up a sweat","relax and unwind"]','["Elite or exclusive language","Intimidating fitness jargon without explanation","Overly corporate or stiff phrasing","Shame-based motivation tactics"]','Budget-conscious fitness seekers aged 18-55, including first-time gym users, fitness beginners, and those intimidated by traditional premium gyms. Also appeals to fitness enthusiasts seeking value and convenience through multi-location access.','["Affordable fitness access without long-term financial commitment","Welcoming, non-intimidating environment to start or resume fitness journey","Professional guidance and support from certified trainers","Convenient access to modern equipment and amenities","Flexibility to cancel membership without penalty","Recovery and wellness amenities beyond basic gym equipment"]','["Intimidation and judgment at traditional gyms","High membership costs and long-term contracts","Lack of personalized guidance for beginners","Limited equipment variety or outdated facilities","Inconvenient locations or limited access","Difficulty maintaining fitness motivation without support"]','{"sentenceLength":"medium","paragraphStyle":"Short to medium paragraphs with a mix of descriptive sentences and benefit-focused statements. Uses conversational tone with occasional rhetorical questions. Typically 2-4 sentences per paragraph, avoiding dense blocks of text.","formatting":"Heavy use of bullet points for equipment lists and amenities. Headlines are benefit-focused rather than feature-focused. Uses short, scannable sections with clear hierarchy. Incorporates bolded key terms and membership tier names (PF BLACK CARD¬Æ, CLASSIC). Calls-to-action are prominent and action-oriented (''Join Now'', ''Select'', ''See Offer Details'').","avoid":["Overly technical fitness terminology without context","Exclusionary language that suggests judgment","Dense paragraphs without visual breaks","Superlatives without supporting details","Formal corporate speak that distances from audience","Shame-based or fear-based messaging"]}',1764690346,1764690346);
INSERT INTO "brand_profiles" VALUES('1764779713357-1idkd8lwz','visualenhancementsinc.com','Visual Enhancements, Inc.','Transforming Spaces with Craftsmanship and Excellence','Since 2005, Visual Enhancements has acquired the knowledge and expertise to bring client visions to life in the Tampa Bay Area. Founded on principles of quality and efficiency, the company has grown to serve both residential and commercial clients with certified contractors and top-tier products.','To prioritize client vision by offering a complete suite of services that deliver exceptional craftsmanship, transforming spaces into stunning environments while enhancing property beauty and value.','Visual Enhancements positions itself as a trusted, certified general contractor specializing in comprehensive home and business improvement solutions. They differentiate through quality craftsmanship, use of premium products (PPG and Sherwin-Williams), attention to detail, and commitment to client communication and satisfaction.','["Complete suite of services under one contractor (painting, flooring, remodeling, stucco repair)","Certified team using latest products and techniques for seamless, stress-free experience","Exceptional craftsmanship with commitment to staying on time and within budget","Free color consultation with interior painting projects","Comprehensive property protection and preparation during work","Trusted by real estate professionals and insurance adjusters for quality and reliability"]','["Professional and trustworthy","Detail-oriented and meticulous","Responsive and communicative","Knowledgeable and expert","Personable and caring"]','{"formal":72,"playful":15,"premium":68,"technical":45,"energetic":58}','["Transforming spaces","Exceptional craftsmanship","Brings your vision to life","Quality and efficiency","Certified team","Stress-free experience","Top-tier products","Let us care for your home","Elevate your space","Seamless experience","Highest standards","Professional and reliab